      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>We can assign different surface and displacement to different faces.</p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"AssigningMaterialsToFaces-\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"250\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644486/metalBand.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129010&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=444&amp;height=250\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644486/metalBand.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129010&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644519\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"metalBand.jpeg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644486\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"2e86d57a-d75c-4c59-bea5-0cf096b78e66\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644486/metalBand.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129010&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=888&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644486/metalBand.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129010&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=444&amp;height=250 1x\"></span> </h3><h3 id=\"AssigningMaterialsToFaces-SettingUpGroup\">Setting Up Group</h3><p>To add a selection of faces to a group:</p><ul><li><p>Change your selection mode to primitives.</p></li><li><p>Select the faces in the Viewport.</p></li><li><p><em>In the Viewport</em>, hit the TAB key and select <strong>Group</strong> to add the faces to the group. </p></li></ul><h3 id=\"AssigningMaterialsToFaces-AssigningMaterialToGroups\">Assigning Material To Groups</h3><p>Add a <strong>Material</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"190\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644486/groups.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433128849&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=190&amp;height=240\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644486/groups.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433128849&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"385\" data-width=\"304\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644507\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"groups.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644486\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c739ecfb-18a3-4ecb-8b6e-78e003c250a8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644486/groups.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433128849&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=304&amp;height=385 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644486/groups.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433128849&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=190&amp;height=240 1x\"></span><p /><p>If you want to assign both Bxdf and displacement shader, you will need to connect to the collect_output both the surface and displacement shaders inside a PxrMaterialBuilder node. </p><p>Assign your group to the material by setting the Material to either a collect vop (see above) or a Bxdf.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"414\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644486/material_parameter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433128849&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=414&amp;height=247\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644486/material_parameter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433128849&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"358\" data-width=\"598\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644510\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"material_parameter.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644486\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e375624e-9283-4a8f-9841-10a8a4d9adaa\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644486/material_parameter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433128849&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=598&amp;height=358 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644486/material_parameter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433128849&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=414&amp;height=247 1x\"></span>"
    }
